snippet.title: Heroes of Hellas 3: Athens - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
One of Alawar Entertainment's match 3 games with a bit of hidden object scenes. And it's part of the Heroes of Hellas series, it seems.

Heroes of Hellas 3: Athens (C) Alawar Entertainment
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/347590/Heroes_of_Hellas_3_Athens/
